{"tid":806352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我只係見到一個事實","createTime":"2018-09-04T14:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T14:54:46.000Z","uid":25787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"363986227d949af6a4c716400d5533fd2bb0a612","tid":806352,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"即係咁，響貿易戰開始之前，都見唔少支那五毛仲吹奏緊一帶一路從同支那製造2025。<br />\n<br />\n但呢排睇返堆支那五毛賤畜好似真係提都唔提呢兩樣野。<br />\n<br />\n我冇睇CCTVB所以唔知呢個官媒仲有冇提。有冇巴打有睇開支那官媒既可以分享下？<br />\n<br />\n好鍾意環球屎報個網既設計，真係一眼睇晒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://opinion.huanqiu.com/editorial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fopinion.huanqiu.com%2Feditorial%2F&d=Z0I2R6kT1vvKUY1NmPO7MTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e28365d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://opinion.huanqiu.com/editorial/</a><br />\n<br />\n「一帶一路」呢4隻字會響社評內文出現既：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.huanqiu.com/s/?q=一帶一路\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.huanqiu.com%2Fs%2F%3Fq%3D%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF&d=Z0I2R6kT1vvKUY1NmPO7MTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=cdb9b748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.huanqiu.com/s/?q=一帶一路</a><br />\n<br />\n好似消失晒咁<br />\n<br />\n好啦，我試下搵埋「2025」（已經唔加支那製造）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.huanqiu.com/s?q=2025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.huanqiu.com%2Fs%3Fq%3D2025&d=Z0I2R6kT1vvKUY1NmPO7MTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a194f461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.huanqiu.com/s?q=2025</a><br />\n<br />\n陰公，一㩒第二頁連CONTENT都冇。<br />\n<br />\n支那五毛賤畜，你地點做野嫁？"}]}